<body>

<h1>CSS Box Model Example</h1>

<p class="labels">Margin → Border → Padding → Content</p>

<div class="box">
    <p>
        This is the CONTENT area of the box model.<br><br>
        Padding creates space inside the border.<br>
        Border surrounds the padding and content.<br>
        Margin creates space outside the box.
    </p>
</div>

